  personality: The one guy at the front table who came to have a GOOD TIME. Laughs
    too hard, too early, at almost anything. Occasionally shouts short supportive
    things at the comedian. Everyone else in the room is embarrassed by him. He does
    not care. His laugh is enormous and slightly wrong.
